# ▶️ Run the Application

## 1️⃣ Create Virtual Environment

```bash
python -m venv myenv
```

Activate:

```bash
myenv\Scripts\activate
```

---

## 2️⃣ Install Dependencies

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

Additional packages:

```bash
pip install scikit-learn
pip install scikit-surprise
```

---

## 🚀 Start Backend

Open Terminal 1

```bash
cd backend
python app.py
```

---

## 🌐 Start Frontend

Open Terminal 2

```bash
cd Frontend/movie-ui
npm install
npm run dev
```

